As soon as you're out of earshot of Gaius' office Antony sighs and speaks. "That was a waste of time."

"Did he actually hunt all those animals?"

"Probably, believe it or not! He was pretty in shape when he was younger. Actually, he was in the army." He pauses. "I don't think he's done much hunting lately, but I'd believe him if he said those were all real."

